#tv-track
Check tv schedule and show. totally customizable and depends upon tvguide.com and only works with tv show.

-----------------------------------------------------------------
#App Needed:-
* curl :- may need to install
* grep :- might already installed
* sed  :- might already installed
* cat  :- might already installed
  
-----------------------------------------------------------------
#Important
user should use specific way in file name 'tv-list.txt'. file name can changed but inside of it should use precisily way it is designed.
For Example:-
this is flash tv series link :- "http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/the-flash/644014/" 
Unique ID(UID) :- should always be place after tv show name colon':' 
####Eg- 'the flash : 644014' without quote
-----------------------------------------------------------------
#Usages:-
       #  Parameter :- 
              *all
              *tv-number or tv show name "use lowercase" don't need to be fullname just a small portion
              *use today
                     *Type 'all'                 :	For all the tv-list
                     *Type 'number / name'       :	For specific tv
                     *Type 'today'               :	to get today's only tv show
-----------------------------------------------------------------
###Can be modified:-
 * filename 'tv-list.txt'

